title: Episode #52 - Dave Williamson & ME
description: Friend and Comedian Dave Williamson and I sit in the Mancave and talk about how he almost got lynched at a Heat game, lived with his wife & kids in an RV for a year, survived Hurricane Andrew, and at the end puts to use all his years of working at a car dealership and tells you a great trick to buying a car!
